# FILE: .../studentDashboard/academicProfile/profileDetails.desc
# ROLE: The Data-Entry & Personalization Engine
# VIBE: Technical / Precise / Form-Focused / Interactive

## 1. THE CORE IDENTITY FORM (Edit Mode)
- **VISUAL:** A 2-column grid with 1px white borders and dark-gray input backgrounds.
- **FIELDS:**
    - **Display Name:** Text input (Ahmed Al-Jassem).
    - **Faculty Select:** Dropdown (Informatics, Architecture, Medicine, etc.).
    - **Academic Year:** Slider or Radio (1st through 5th + Graduate).
    - **Personal Bio:** A Markdown-supported textarea for the "Challenge Every Day" personal story.
- **WONDER FEATURE:** A "Live Preview" card on the right that updates in real-time as the student types.

## 2. THE SKILL & DISCIPLINE SELECTOR (Multi-Tag)
- **LOGIC:** Links directly to the "12 Main Disciplines" found in the `freelanceHome.desc`.
- **INPUT:** A searchable tag-cloud where students can select their expertise (e.g., Programming, AI, Design).
- **FREELANCE TOGGLE:** A prominent switch: **[ 💼 Enable Freelancer Mode ]**. 
    - *Note:* If toggled ON, it triggers the requirement for the $5 subscription and ShamCash verification.

## 3. THE SOCIAL & PROFESSIONAL NODES
- **EXTERNAL LINKS:** Input fields for connecting the profile to the outside world.
    - [ 💻 GitHub ] | [ 🔗 LinkedIn ] | [ 📸 Portfolio/Drive ].
    - [ 📱 WhatsApp ] (For direct client/student communication).
- **VALIDATION:** Checks for "https://" to ensure the links are functional before saving.

## 4. ACCOUNT SECURITY & PRIVACY SETTINGS
- **PASSWORD RESET:** A secure section to update credentials with "Strength Meter" (0-100%).
- **DATA VISIBILITY:** Individual toggles for each data point:
    - [ 👁️ Show my GPA/Grades? ] -> ON/OFF.
    - [ 👁️ Show my Email? ] -> ON/OFF.
    - [ 👁️ Show my XP Level? ] -> ON/OFF.

## 5. DOCUMENT & ID UPLOAD (The Verification Step)
- **FILE ZONE:** A drag-and-drop terminal specifically for the **University Student ID**.
- **STATUS INDICATOR:** - `[ ⏳ Pending ]`: If recently uploaded.
    - `[ ✅ Verified ]`: If the Admin approved it via `userAccountManager.desc`.
- **GUIDE:** "Upload a clear photo of your ID to unlock the [ ✅ ] badge and Freelance Hub."

## 6. THE STICKY SUBMIT HUD (Bottom)
- **PRIMARY ACTION:** [ 💾 Save Changes ] — Triggers a "Success" pulse animation.
- **SECONDARY ACTION:** [ 🗑️ Reset to Default ] — Clears all unsaved edits.
- **FOOTER NOTE:** "Changes to your Faculty or ID may require re-verification by the HalabUnver Admin."